    "<p>Director of the Galleria degli Uffizi, Florence, 1950 to 1956; contributed to wave of post-WWII scholarship on the Romanesque.": [],
    "Salvini studied under <a href=\"/salmim\">Mario Salmi</a> at the University of Florence in 1929.": [
        [
